        <updateDate>2012-08-29T16:31:05Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Children of Fallen Heroes Scholarship Act of 2012 - Amends the Higher Educaton Act of 1965 to eliminate the expected family contribution used in determining Pell Grant eligibility in the case of a student applicant whose parent or guardian died as a result of performing service as a police officer, firefighter, or other public safety officer.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
